{"tid":2311761,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"亂了方寸 - 李純恩","createTime":"2020-12-04T10:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T10:29:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a4db761c450853f0403687ed933e931697ae85ba","tid":2311761,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T10:21:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201204/2ILZAGKFEZER7LFSA2LHO47UJ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201204%2F2ILZAGKFEZER7LFSA2LHO47UJ4%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGA2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=3c7980a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201204%2F2ILZAGKFEZER7LFSA2LHO47UJ4%2F&h=f8eeb9df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201204/2ILZAGKFEZER7LFSA2LHO47UJ4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n亂了方寸 - 李純恩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vxx4aX1u4-oBPyU72f4iqGp78S0=/5324x3550/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UYIXTODYXVCMPOMTWNRJFKMVZI.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fvxx4aX1u4-oBPyU72f4iqGp78S0%3D%2F5324x3550%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUYIXTODYXVCMPOMTWNRJFKMVZI.JPG&h=13591d68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港疫情第四波爆發，各類禁聚措施收緊，但之前的漏洞太大，亡羊補牢，不知要費多大的氣力才能補得牢。這天朋友說現在的無源頭確診個案越來越多，真是奇怪。我說這並不奇怪，所謂無源頭，可能有許多是確診者不方便透露源頭而已，比如去過的地方不想讓人知道，幫襯過的人不想讓人知道，問起來，個個都說自己老老實實待在家裏，不知怎麼一來就染病了。無源頭其實都有源頭，源頭讓一些確診者吞進了肚子，就消失了。<br />\n<br />\n做餐飲業的朋友叫苦連天，本來叫作已見到了曙光，這一個多月來生意剛剛見了點起色，如今吃飯人數又限至兩位，曙光一閃而過，噩夢重臨。前陣子有位好不容易挺到現在的餐廳老闆說，前兩個月形勢最惡劣的時候，他曾想過關門大吉，一了百了。但後來又咬了咬牙，終於挺到六人一枱，生意回升，以為劫難已過，料不到瘟神捲土重來，他說已有心理準備，說不定就死在這一波下。<br />\n<br />\n前兩天跟朋友行完山去。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"b980065aa675110bf153752c78e27edfbf945db4","tid":2311761,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T10:29:07.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>根本就係借武漢肺炎呢個弱傷風去追蹤所有香港市民行蹤</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}